summary: AN ORDINANCE Relating to the Water Department authorizing the sale by Real Estate Contract (marked Exhibit "A") and conveyance by Fulfillment Quit Claim Deed (marked Exhibit "B") of a portion of real property commonly known as the Lake Youngs Aqueduct Right-of-Way (LYA R/W) located in Section 22, Township 22 North, Range 6 East, W.M., King County, Washington, to John D.
